12/x 

To finish off, we give a shout-out and our thanks to our amazing community, for being part of this journey with us.

Get ready to build! 🏗️🌐

11/x

Some planned features include:

- Apartments on marketplaces will be updated to show off apartment designs
- NFT furniture
- Multiplayer coming soon
- Improved mobile support
- Animated NFT support
- Quest system

Just to name a few.

10/x

We are extremely proud to launch the first iteration of the Apartment Builder and are excited to see how it will be put to use. 

While this is a demo we are proud of, this is just the beginning and more features will be added over time.

9/x

When designing apartments, the sky is the limit. Our group of testers has already come up with various different builds. Home theaters, offices, art galleries, studios, shops, and much much more.

We are excited to see what the entirety of the community will come up with! https://t.co/9sqjBdDfxm

8/x

NPC functionality allows you to add NPCs to your apartment. To put it bluntly, you can add your NFTs that are integrated with Worldwide Webb to hang out in your apartment as characters or pets

In the gif below, we see a bunch of Mooncats running around an apartment. https://t.co/WlnbpOi8nZ

7/x

NFT display is also possible. We use a pixel shader rendering to allow holders to display NFTs within their apartments. This allows curation of galleries, shows, or just plain decoration and flexibility. https://t.co/VMuNihfPcw

6/x

The apartment builder is launching with hundreds of different items that can be placed within rooms. Some of them have different variations, and you can even place certain items on top of each other, for example, a vase on a desk. https://t.co/kYMOEZAEfp

5/x

The builder lets you define the room floor plan. The walls and floors of Each room are editable. There are no restrictions for room designs, other than that all rooms have to be connected to one another.

4/x

Apartment selection lets users choose which apartment they want to design. There are four types of apartments:

- Small
- Medium
- Large
- Penthouse

For now, the main difference is that larger apartments have bigger sizes, allowing larger builds. https://t.co/1O8csfmMAQ

3/x

The builder features a “Free build mode” that is accessible by anyone, as a “Try-before-you-buy” feature. Free build mode builds are not part of the game, but they let people that don’t own apartments try the builder out, and get creative with different builds.

2/x

The Apartment Builder is the first step towards the tools we want to release in order to allow users to build out the game universe and give apartment holders utility.

This is a big milestone in our project, so we are very excited to release the builder.

1/x

The Apartment Builder is coming on the 28th of February. This is going to be our biggest release yet.

Below is an overview of the different functionalities that the Apartment Builder offers.

Get ready to design your apartments! 🧵 https://t.co/9tnJ7luni6

Apartments are core to the game, so the builder lets players design their apartments & shape the world.
